.SH NAME
.PP
while \- Simple shell loop.
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Read stdin and perform an action on every line:
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
while\ read\ line;\ do\ echo\ "$line";\ done
\f[]
.fi
.PP
Execute a command forever once every second:
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
while\ :;\ do\ {{command}};\ sleep\ 1;\ done
\f[]
.fi
